enableDiscovery

public boolean enableDiscovery()
Check if SAML Discovery Profile should be enabled. If more than one metadata file exists, discovery should be enabled, and this method will return true.

getFirstMetadata

public IdpMetadata.Metadata getFirstMetadata()
Get the first registered metadata. This method should only be used when enableDiscovery() returns true, as the metadata list is not ordered.
